 HOW TO PLAY

 Boot from disk (in drive DF0: !), or type "MEGA-TYPHOON"  at  the  CLI-
 prompt.
 Hit the SPACE Key for smart bombs.
 Hit the ESCAPE Key mouse button to exit.
 Hit the P Key to pause the game.


 ===========================================================================

              A B O U T    M E G A - T Y P H O O N

 ===========================================================================


    Enjoy the first REAL arcade-like shoot-em-up ever made for
                       the amiga computer



 MISSION:   insert coin.

            destroy them all ...

            (good luck ! ;-)



 KEYS:     <SPACE> or second button  Smart Bomb

           <P>                       Pause

           <ESCAPE>                  Abort Mission



 WEAPONS & EXTRAS:
           
           <S>          Spread Shot

           <L>          Sinus Laser

           <H>          Homing Missiles

           <M>          Power Missiles

           <B>          Smart Bomb
           
           <P>          Get Full Weapon

           <1UP>        Extra Life


           To increase weapon power, collect bonus items
           of THE SAME TYPE successively.

           Modify power of the sinus laser by varying
           the fire-button frequency


 TECHNICAL FEATURES:


            *   more than 100 objects moving on screen 
                at the same time

            *   50 (!) frames per second (fps)
                (all conventional games with comparable number,
                size and complexity of moving objects run at 17 
                or at most 25 fps only )

            *   Full performance on ALL AMIGAS (including A1000,A500)

            *   pioneering new graphics engine featuring
                64 BOB's, 48 Sprites, 16 Colors

            *   copper driven blitter
 
            *   virtual sprite engine 
 
            *   virtual playfield scrolling

            *   asynchronuous multi-process animation algorithm 

            *   animation/control process separation 
 
  In other words:

     The fastest arcade action game ever made for the AMIGA ! 

